Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:04.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甲冑是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:09.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上的時候 傷口就像假的一樣不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:16.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:18.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這股在體內沸騰的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:28.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體中有什麼狂暴的東西湧現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 身 體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是 的這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 血 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:35.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:37.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:38.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 骨 髓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻上你的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:44.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 生 命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甲冑的形狀在...
Comment: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.15,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/------START-------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:31.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你的真正實力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:34.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣才有粉碎的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的龐大身體打飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:50.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的蠻力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:54.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是剛才那個男人的攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:02.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然弄碎了我這連炮彈都能擋住的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:07.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個手舞大劍身穿甲冑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是人類可以做出的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:23.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙義肢上裝著大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一直就像怪物一樣強悍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天感覺不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:32.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻假手是大炮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:37.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有危險 如果繼續那樣的戰鬥下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才開始你是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的格斯先生傷口並未癒合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:46.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感覺不到傷口的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:51.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是矮人製作成的咒物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,狂戰士的甲冑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,狂戰士的 甲冑?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:03.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上那副甲冑後 再與寄宿其中的不祥之氣同步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就會如同鬼神一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:09.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被強烈的感情控制 忘記痛苦和恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:13.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人類為了不讓自己的肉體受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,會無意識地設定力量的上限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛 是防止自己的肉體受傷的警報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:26.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,失去痛感的人 會發揮出不得了的力量和速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然後超出人體的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入生命的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:40.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 格斯他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 氣的活動太劇烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我的念話無法傳達過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是黑色劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我等的宿敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼以我這會心一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:10.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這次單挑是你勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看來傳言不假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你是遠超其上的超級戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:31.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 從現在開始我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是為了吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作光之鷹的使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,當你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,龍?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:53.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使用使徒被授予的力量 埋葬黑色劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正面打中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:01.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 竟然擋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:05.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人類把使徒的攻擊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不承認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:20.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比鋼鐵還堅硬的我的鋼王的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,龜裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:37.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 剛才手腳轉向相反的方向了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是甲冑的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:43.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甲冑在補給折斷的手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,貫穿血肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,餵食骨髓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:50.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說以前那副甲冑的持有者就像那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,整個身體被甲冑的鐵齒蠶食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:56.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,直到全身的骨頭碎裂 全身的血液噴干還仍然戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最後斷氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼把那麼危險的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,給瀕死的格斯穿上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:08.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為 為了讓同伴活下去 總要有犧栍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:13.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 因為我的錯 又要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:17.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人 為什麼 為什麼把那種東西...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:22.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你去做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是只有你這個魔法師才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我還不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,內心又混亂 魔術會...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:39.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚自身的稚嫩 知曉沉溺於力量的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 現在的你才能夠做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:46.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那身處力量的亂流中的劍士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要向他展現道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 做怎麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去把格斯先生帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,試試看吧 師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託是 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:11.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然第二次擋住了我這樣形態發出的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:14.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還讓我受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去找魔女的人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也不能閒著不做事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像你也很棘手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:35.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對使徒來說 單挑根本就無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在變身的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:48.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個觸感 有四五根肋骨斷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥方式漸漸不像人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對 那簡直就像...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊有好像很好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一有什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就抱上史爾基逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:20.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:29.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是寄生在甲冑上的憎惡的亂流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被這種東西吞食的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人的自我會支離破碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:50.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生的憎惡 增幅甲冑的氣但不是憎惡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:52.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生就在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我能辦到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:02.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從這麼巨大的亂流中把人救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是失手我也會被這亂流吞沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是猶豫的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,光之泡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生記憶的片段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像燈火一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成群的暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 什麼啊 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,捲進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 這是格斯先生的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人的護符防止了自我的崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:29.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 不能隨波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,隨波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:35.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對 你會因為你而消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,會被這領域拉進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,I K Σ  Λ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fsp-42\pos(995,1015)}ии
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,HБАЯьыъц
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使徒 敵人 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能怎樣都可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:11:59.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你旅行的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了怎樣都可以的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:10.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的靈魂是不會如此破爛不堪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:11.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:12.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:23.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:43.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:47.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回憶起來她的名字是卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喀絲 卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是 格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是烙印的劍士 格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:01.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是保護烙印的女子卡思嘉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,承受我的灼熱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:22.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:23.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:39.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:51.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好慘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做得不錯 史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這片森林也撐不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:41.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,靈樹燒毀的話這岸領域也就會關閉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:50.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是古老东西飄蕩的时间的狭间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:54.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我和這棵樹的壽命也太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算陽光再如何舒適
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:02.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,新的東西也不能永遠停留在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,離巢的時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:11.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,離開這裡 找到自己的道路吧 我得意的弟子喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:15.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和你相處的時間雖然短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:21.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻是我一生中最為安逸的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:30.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 黑色劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:41.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身為火龍的我也無法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,生命只是變了形式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在你夢中再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:53.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能否抓住眼前的命運就靠你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:58.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福你的成長 我親愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了 我的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:26.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是抵抗組織的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:45.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是米特蘭軍阿古羅騎士團團長拉班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 拉班大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:52.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,團長竟然親自前來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:58.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,們至今的所作所為 作為武人深感敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:04.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 抵抗組織只是空有其名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:09.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在暗地裡倉皇逃命已經很吃力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在溫達姆城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:16.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很難想像還是現世 已經化為魔都了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抵抗者全部處死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住的人 不論身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:26.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都當成戰奴送上戰場了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,女人們被關在城堡裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:33.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被用於庫夏人的奇怪儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:39.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下老弱病殘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,何等可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:46.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還有一線希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夏洛特公主還健在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:55.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聰說被關在那個再生之塔的頂層了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此話當真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:17:59.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,千真萬確
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:04.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為了得到這條情報 我們失去了很多的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人沒事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:10.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,皇家的血脈沒有斷就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:18.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拉班大人 我們被困在都城不知道外界的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:22.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想確認一個傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹 在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:28.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拉班大人 這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個怪物究竟是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:46.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,庫夏人的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:53.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,庫夏人用魔法控制那些半人半獸的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說剛親眼得見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:09.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時城市被大霧籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:16.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被霧召喚而來 怪物們開始在街上橫行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:21.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,市民們深感恐懼 都躲在屋裡不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,箭? 從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:06.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,溫達姆的市民們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在暫且躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:14.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天捲走城中瘴氣的強風會吹起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還身負任務 就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,躲藏忍耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:27.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等到鷹帶來風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:10.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:17.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小孩啊 不過就是一個大水坑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:19.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:33.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:42.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:52.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體可沒有那麼纖弱 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:58.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還是把那身甲冑脫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:23:01.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,起碼靜養四五天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:04.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本來我就差不多睡了一個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:10.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說不想戰鬥的時候那樣完全感不到疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:13.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多虧它旅行才能繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:15.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:16.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是被詛咒的鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:19.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再戰鬥的話不知何時又會失控
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:22.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到那時候 不是還有一個可靠的魔法師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:26.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都是精靈 現在就一起黏黏糊糊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:28.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:31.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再發生那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:35.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算現在不能保證性命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:38.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:46.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為再也見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:52.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在陽光下 如此的閒逸
